										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><b>Africa Tech Summit Nairobi has announced the 10 African tech ventures that will showcase their solutions to an audience of industry experts, investors and fellow innovators on February 14-15.</b></p>
<p><a href="https://www.africatechsummit.com/nairobi/"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Africa Tech Summit Nairobi</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> is a leading African tech event providing insight and networking with the African tech ecosystem, bringing together tech leaders, MNOs, banks, international investors, entrepreneurs, governments, trade bodies, media and leading ventures to drive investment and business in African tech.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The sixth edition of the event, powered by global account receivable and expense management solution </span><a href="https://www.raenest.com/"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Raenest</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">, will take place in February, connecting over 1,000 African and international industry leaders, investors, and startups from across the African tech ecosystem.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The annual Investment Showcase is a cornerstone of Africa Tech Summit, allowing selected ventures to showcase their products and services to a diverse audience of local and international investors and tech leaders</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">More than 250 entries were received from various countries across Africa, with 10 startups eventually selected, spanning fintech, agri-tech, e-commerce, Web3, and climate-tech. They are all looking to raise funding ranging from US$500,000 to US$15 million. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Four of the selected companies are from Kenya: </span><a href="https://cktxq04.na1.hs-sales-engage.com/Ctc/R+23284/ckTXq04/Jks2-6qcW69sMD-6lZ3mqW2z0kNx3qsKrNW49Jbd18cTYDNW18TMdT85nGP6W1DZCS86hDJ5KW5JJN2L4qmxdvVJphf81W6mpQW2DHX-98nzx5dW5HzqCc7n2-j3W23f3BV4Z-KB4W6Vnwf_86y66nW7qQPN61GgdJpN2rdjjkJHJdmW8bM41b2Fl2z1VghKR775bc53W5HdDLT1x52crW92hJHn5jgH9VW3TWtzB1nSwDTW2dKncg8rSNHZW8xGhPY1Shgy0W1qd7vN4sx7-Vf5kpL4404"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Node Bio</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">, which utilises cutting-edge plant science to develop crop treatment that effectively combat the adverse effects of climate change; </span><a href="https://cktxq04.na1.hs-sales-engage.com/Ctc/R+23284/ckTXq04/Jks2-6qcW69sMD-6lZ3n_W923Hhm5PCtlRW6J8BH88mj2YGN4ZHRT1pnpZpW3B0RFl6RWv09W2TWD4d2gKWpCW8CwNsJ2rRB1xW150ys-1pTHVRW1h9p2l6CFNC0W25R72P5_DnrmW7jpKR_2hh_M8W81T-Xq3RsfclW3nnts56bGxKNN779Fz8z8qCLW4Ljrqn8tRS3hW79_vBr2WpmxxN6qFyP0M-SRwW47K7Hc30skVBW4hdJB86qt2HzF7CgvFNWsPDW9l3xmz5YSjKSf7Xn-Qg04"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Tausi App</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">, a beauty tech company that is leveraging technology to link beauticians to potential customers; </span><a href="https://cktxq04.na1.hs-sales-engage.com/Ctc/R+23284/ckTXq04/JkM2-6qcW6N1vHY6lZ3q7W7Gs1nL2qq6kGW88lwfy3-Fkj3W4SPVD47fqc6PW6smxXT2ms-xGW2jt1P96BLK0ZW3hqL8V4W4svHW3Yjwcb1W91W3W3YBs_b9drWrgN1WYbfMfLHYgN6Q_J8B6qCB0W54CkqC1y2VPdW8bG_tz7lfJFRW6_gLpC51MySKW1BPNWn1rHd0LW1bgZmg6tcPyyW5V9Dd-9jbSl8W8Ts9bY1BcVPSW97XTR12dyHZlW8CrcHz7xfXv3VF7QKw6ScYgKW5K_brc7jwx3VVfcyKT24Yjbtf38pK2H04"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Peercarbon</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">, a climate fintech startup leveraging granular emissions data and cutting-edge sustainable finance technology to empower African SMEs; and </span><a href="https://cktxq04.na1.hs-sales-engage.com/Ctc/R+23284/ckTXq04/JkM2-6qcW6N1vHY6lZ3prN7Z22zs4gW4XW10LDpP8vtDF2Tr7sy7LJTHfV48cxW662FXKW2pRGL874p4MWW8-fTFF8-qdp7W4sKzq