										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The meme coin landscape is experiencing a resurgence, with established players like Dogecoin and Shiba Inu maintaining their dominance in the market while new coins like Pepe and Dogwifhat experience recent price surges. These new coins, alongside the “Boost-to-Earn coin </span><a href="https://apemax.co/?ref=da_20"><span style="font-weight: 400;">ApeMax</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">, are quickly gaining traction because of their innovative features.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Based on information gathered from diverse sources such as top blockchain news sites and official coin websites, this article will take a closer look at the top meme coins by market cap capturing the attention of Web3 enthusiasts in 2024. </span></p>
<p><a href="http://apemax.co/?ref=da_1"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-34714 size-full" src="http://disrupt-africa.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Top-new-meme-coins-in-2024.png" alt="" width="1456" height="180" srcset="https://old.disruptafrica.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Top-new-meme-coins-in-2024.png 1456w, https://old.disruptafrica.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Top-new-meme-coins-in-2024-300x37.png 300w, https://old.disruptafrica.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Top-new-meme-coins-in-2024-1024x127.png 1024w, https://old.disruptafrica.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Top-new-meme-coins-in-2024-150x19.png 150w, https://old.disruptafrica.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Top-new-meme-coins-in-2024-450x56.png 450w, https://old.disruptafrica.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Top-new-meme-coins-in-2024-1200x148.png 1200w, https://old.disruptafrica.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Top-new-meme-coins-in-2024-768x95.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1456px) 100vw, 1456px" /></a></p>
<p><b>Trending New Meme Coins and Top Meme Coins by Market Cap</b><b></b></p>
<ul>
<li aria-level="1"><b>ApeMax (APEMAX)</b></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Leading the charge is ApeMax, a unique meme coin that introduces the innovative </span><a href="https://apemax.co/?ref=da_20"><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8220;Boost-to-Earn&#8221; staking</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> system. This feature allows token holders to possibly earn rewards by staking and boosting their favorite entities. </span></p>
<p><a href="https://apemax.co/?ref=da_20"><span style="font-weight: 400;">ApeMax</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> eligible buyers can also enjoy immediate token access post-purchase, a feature uncommon in most meme coin presales. This instant utility empowers holders to engage in boost staking. In addition to its unique tokenomics, ApeMax is currently in a growing presale phase, offering early buyers discounts through </span><a href="https://apemax.co/?ref=da_20&amp;lootbox=true"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Early Bird Loot Boxes</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> for a limited time.</span><b></b></p>
<ul>
<li aria-level="1"><b>Dogecoin (DOGE)</b></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">As the pioneer of meme coins, Dogecoin started as a jest in 2013 but has evolved into a significant player in the crypto market. Its association with Elon Musk and dedicated token holders contribute to its substantial market capitalization, reaching $11 billion. </span><b></b></p>
<ul>
<li aria-level="1"><b>Shiba Inu (SHIB)</b></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Renowned as a &#8220;Dogecoin killer&#8221;, Shiba Inu gained fame in 2021 and continues to be a popular choice among meme coin enthusiasts. Shiba Inu introduced Shibarium, a Layer 2 blockchain on Ethereum, aiming to address issues like gas fees and congestion. SHIB has a whopping market cap exceeding $5 billion. </span><b></b></p>
<ul>
<li aria-level="1"><b>Pepe Coin (PEPE)</b></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Pepe Coin, inspired by the renowned “Pepe the Frog” meme, became popular in early 2023. Pepe has a market cap of roughly $477 million. </span><b></b></p>
<ul>
<li aria-level="1"><b>Floki (FLOKI)</b></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Inspired by Elon Musk’s Shiba Inu dog, Floki boasts an extensive ecosystem, including the immersive metaverse game “Valhalla” and FlokiFi, its native DEX. Floki has a market cap of approximately $278 million.</span></p>
<p><a href="http://apemax.co/?ref=da_1"><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-34715" src="http://disrupt-africa.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Next-big-crypto-coin.png" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://old.disruptafrica.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Next-big-crypto-coin.png 1920w, https://old.disruptafrica.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Next-big-crypto-coin-300x169.png 300w, https://old.disruptafrica.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Next-big-crypto-coin-1024x576.png 1024w, https://old.disruptafrica.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Next-big-crypto-coin-1536x864.png 1536w, https://old.disruptafrica.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Next-big-crypto-coin-150x84.png 150w, https://old.disruptafrica.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Next-big-crypto-coin-450x253.png 450w, https://old.disruptafrica.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Next-big-crypto-coin-1200x675.png 1200w, https://old.disruptafrica.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Next-big-crypto-coin-768x432.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></a></p>
<ul>
<li aria-level="1"><b>Memecoin by 9gag (MEME)</b></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Operating on the Ethereum-based ERC-20 network, Memecoin is a creation of the 9gag group and Web3 firm Memeland. Memecoin aims to carve its niche in the competitive meme coin landscape. </span><a href="https://coinmarketcap.com/currencies/meme/"><span style="font-weight: 400;">MEME</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> has a market cap of $216 million. </span><b></b></p>
<ul>
<li aria-level="1"><b>Bonk (BONK)</b></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Bonk emerged on the Solana blockchain in December 2022, gaining quick traction through its association with Solana meme culture. Bonk, like ApeMax, distinguishes itself by leveraging a blockchain platform with lower transaction costs. </span><a href="https://bonkcoin.com/"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Bonk</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;"> has a market cap of about $750 million. </span></p>
<p><b>Why Buyers Consider a Coin’s Market Cap</b></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Market capitalization can play a role in evaluating a cryptocurrency’s size, providing a comprehensive comparison across different tokens. Buyers utilize market cap as a key statistic to gauge the market dominance of a particular cryptocurrency.</span></p>
<p><b>Which Meme Coin will Explode in 2024?</b></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Predicting which meme coin will explode in 2024 is challenging, given the numerous factors influencing cryptocurrency success. Market sentiment, project fundamentals, community engagement, and unforeseen events all contribute to a coin&#8217;s trajectory in the crypto space.</span></p>
